scene_description_enriched: A group of armored soldiers surround a young man in a blue tunic and yellow sleeves, who stands with his hands clasped in prayer. One soldier on horseback, wearing ornate armor, raises a sword as if to strike. The scene takes place outdoors in a grassy landscape with some rocky outcrops. The soldiers are armed with spears and wear helmets and mail armor. A banner with an inscription is visible near the praying figure.
